{"tid":1983819,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅持返工】新蒲崗文員獲批病假仍上班　上司勸阻不果報警求助","createTime":"2020-04-22T05:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T06:38:03.000Z","uid":187957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a34d627c41f42d5b24eed271b5aed614034a5a0c","tid":1983819,"uid":187957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:24:40.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀肺炎疫情持續，一名女文員帶病上班，上司勸阻不果報警求助！警方指今日（22日）早上10時許，接獲一名68歲姓連男子報案，他指其58歲姓潘女員工，拒放病假遂報警。警員接報到場，女事主自行離開公司及回家，暫列雜項處理。《香港01》記者到現埸了解，涉事公司從事塑膠機械製造業。有職員表示，女事主從事文職工作，她非患上新型冠狀肺炎。對於女事主拒放病假的原因，有職員透露：「佢有責任感！」<br />\n<br />\n根據勞工處資料顯示，如僱員感染新型冠狀病毒，僱主須根據《僱傭條例》及有關僱傭合約給予僱員病假。另外，如僱主在僱員放取有薪病假期間解僱員工，即屬違法，最高可被罰款10萬元，同時僱主須支付該名員工的解僱代通知金等等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/463952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F463952&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8sljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=214fe71b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/463952</a>"},{"pid":"b8abcb73d58bf6bb03d6dae6fea08c729638cd77","tid":1983819,"uid":187957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"報警要個員工放sick leave <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb0ee390b6840f20bef0e3dec4601da299d43d","tid":1983819,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"成件事最奇怪係個老闆因為d乜嘢原因 會玩到報狗拉9個文員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定唔只係射波咁簡單"},{"pid":"7fc60081d52866892fcd75fb4584e858d9a3179d"